<i>noun</i>: 반딧불이 [반디뿌리/반딛뿌리], 반딧불 [반디뿔/반딛뿔], 반디 [반디], 개똥벌레 [개ː똥벌레] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>반딧불이 [반디뿌리/반딛뿌리]</dt><br>
<dd>firefly; lightning bug</dd><br>
<dd>꽁무니에서 빛을 내며 날아다니는 곤충.</dd><br>
<dd>A flying insect that emits light from its rear.</dd><br>
<dt>반딧불 [반디뿔/반딛뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firefly light</dd><br>
<dd>반딧불이의 꽁무니에서 나는 불빛.</dd><br>
<dd>The light produced from the abdomen of a firefly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. firefly</dd><br>
<dd>꽁무니에서 빛을 내며 날아다니는 곤충.</dd><br>
<dd>An insect that flies, giving off light from its abdomen.</dd><br>
<dt>반디 [반디]</dt><br>
<dd>firefly; lightning bug</dd><br>
<dd>꽁무니에서 빛을 내며 날아다니는 곤충.</dd><br>
<dd>A flying insect that emits light from its rear.</dd><br>
<dt>개똥벌레 [개ː똥벌레]</dt><br>
<dd>firefly</dd><br>
<dd>꽁무니에서 빛을 내며 날아다니는 곤충.</dd><br>
<dd>An insect which flies with a light from its back end.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>